# GitLab CE Instance Setup on Kubernetes

**TTM Technologies — Hillsborough RKE2 Cluster**  
**Date:** April 2026  
**Author:** Alhaji Suma

-----

## Overview

This document covers the deployment of a GitLab Community Edition instance on the Hillsborough RKE2 Kubernetes cluster. The instance is accessible at `gitlab.apps.ttmtech.com` and is LDAP integrated against TTM Active Directory.

-----

## Prerequisites

### Cluster Details

|Component        |Value                                                    |
|-----------------|---------------------------------------------------------|
|Cluster Type     |RKE2 v1.35.0                                             |
|Control Plane    |aamhilcp01, aamhilcp02, aamhilcp03 (RHEL 9.7)            |
|Workers          |aamhilwk01, aamhilwk02, aamhilwk03, aamhilwk04 (RHEL 9.7)|
