## Step 7 — HAProxy Configuration

Add the following to `/etc/haproxy/haproxy.cfg` on the HAProxy server:

```
# ACLs
acl is_gitlab        hdr(host) -i gitlab.apps.ttmtech.com
acl is_registry      hdr(host) -i registry.apps.ttmtech.com
acl is_minio_api     hdr(host) -i minio.apps.ttmtech.com minio-api.apps.ttmtech.com
acl is_minio_console hdr(host) -i minio-console.apps.ttmtech.com

# Routing
use_backend gitlab_backend        if is_gitlab
use_backend registry_backend      if is_registry
use_backend minio_api_backend     if is_minio_api
use_backend minio_console_backend if is_minio_console

# Backends
backend gitlab_backend
    mode http
    balance roundrobin
    http-request set-header Host gitlab.apps.ttmtech.com
    server wk01 10.45.10.171:443 check ssl verify none maxconn 700
    server wk02 10.45.10.172:443 check ssl verify none maxconn 700
