## Troubleshooting

### Check Pod Status

```bash
kubectl get pods -n gitlab
kubectl get pods -n minio-system
```

### Check Logs

```bash
kubectl logs -n gitlab -l app=webservice --tail=50
kubectl logs -n gitlab -l app=sidekiq --tail=50
```

### Test LDAP

```bash
# Test bind from control plane
ldapsearch -x -H ldap://aamhildc01.ttmtech.local \
  -D "svc.ldap@ttmtech.local" \
  -w "<password>" \
  -b "DC=TTMTECH,DC=local" \
  "(sAMAccountName=<username>)" dn

# Test from toolbox pod
kubectl exec -it <toolbox-pod> -n gitlab -- bash
gitlab-rake gitlab:ldap:check
```

### Retrieve Root Password

```bash
kubectl get secret gitlab-gitlab-initial-root-password \
  -n gitlab \
  -o jsonpath='{.data.password}' | base64 -d
```

### Common Issues

|Issue                |Resolution                                       |
|---------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
|Ingress returning 404|Patch ingress class to `nginx`                   |
|Registry pod crashing|Check CoreDNS resolves minio-api.apps.ttmtech.com|
|LDAP login failing   |Verify bind DN and password with ldapsearch      |
|ImagePullBackOff     |Image not in internal registry — mirror it       |
|PVC stuck in Pending |Check Longhorn disk capacity on worker nodes     |